         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="MS-B-00005-B-000-00016"/><date>6.</date></dateline><salute rend="center">lieber D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>!</salute></opener><p>Ich habe mit Ihnen u <rs type="person" ref="#pmb11740"><hi rend="latintype">Loris</hi></rs> in einer lit. Angelegenheit zu<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>prechen u. ko<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>e
               deshalb morgen <date>Samstag</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><time>3 U. NM.</time> mit <rs type="person" ref="#pmb11740">L.</rs> zu Ihnen. Bitte,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>eien Sie daheim.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t<lb/><signed>Bahr</signed></closer></div>
